natural_language: The system will not install updates unless there is enough disk space and the update is available.
ground_truth: SOFTWARE_INSTALL UNLESS NOT ENOUGH_DISK_SPACE OR NOT UPDATE_AVAILABLE

natural_language: The application will not launch unless the operating system is updated and the user is logged in.
ground_truth: APPLICATION_LAUNCH UNLESS NOT OPERATING_SYSTEM_UPDATED OR NOT USER_LOGGED_IN

natural_language: The feature will not be enabled unless the user is authenticated and the feature is available.
ground_truth: FEATURE_ENABLED UNLESS NOT USER_AUTHENTICATED OR NOT FEATURE_AVAILABLE

natural_language: The service will not start automatically unless auto mode is selected and the service is configured.
ground_truth: SERVICE_START UNLESS NOT AUTO_MODE_SELECTED OR NOT SERVICE_CONFIGURED

natural_language: The device will not enter sleep mode unless there have been 5 minutes of inactivity and the device is idle.
ground_truth: SLEEP_MODE UNLESS INACTIVITY_LESS_THAN_5MIN OR NOT DEVICE_IDLE
llm_output: DEVICE_IN_SLEEP_MODE IMPLIES (NOT DEVICE_ACTIVE FOR 300 SECONDS) AND NOT DEVICE_BUSY

natural_language: Notifications will not appear unless do not disturb mode is disabled and the phone is switched on.
The backup will not proceed unless the storage device is connected and backup is enabled.
ground_truth: BACKUP_PROCEED UNLESS NOT STORAGE_CONNECTED OR NOT BACKUP_ENABLED

natural_language: The system will not reboot unless all critical processes have completed and a reboot is requested.
ground_truth: SYSTEM_REBOOT UNLESS CRITICAL_PROCESSES_RUNNING OR NOT REBOOT_REQUESTED

natural_language: The settings will not be saved unless the form is validated and the user has confirmed.
ground_truth: SETTINGS_SAVED UNLESS NOT FORM_VALIDATED OR NOT USER_CONFIRMED

natural_language: The connection will not be established unless the network is available and a connection is requested.
ground_truth: CONNECTION_ESTABLISHED UNLESS NOT NETWORK_AVAILABLE OR NOT CONNECTION_REQUESTED
